window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The very first Spellmonger anthology! Includes two audio exclusive stories, <i>Stonesinger</i> and <i>The Ugliest Maid in Castal</i>.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Contains four previously unpublished Spellmonger short stories, \"The Wizard of Birchroot Bridge\", \"The Secret of Westwood Hall\", \"The Road to Sevendor\", and \"The Iron Ring\", including the full and complete versions of the previously published <i>The River Mists of Talry</i>, <i>Victory Soup</i>, and <i>The Spellmonger's Wedding</i>. Enjoy these scraps from the Spellmonger's table and the fantasy world of Callidore - where they put the evil back into medieval!</p>"; 
